hat%20the%20riders%20know%20what%20the%20day%20in%20the%20life%20of%20a%20driver%20is%2C%26quot%3B%20Inada%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGigU%20launched%20its%20paid%20app%20for%20drivers%20in%20the%20US%20in%20May.%20It's%20one%20of%20a%20few%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fuber-lyft-gigu-mystro-rideshare-apps-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ethird-party%20apps%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20says%20it%20helps%20gig%20workers%20parse%20ride%20and%20delivery%20offers%20to%20determine%20which%20are%20the%20best%20use%20of%20their%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUber%20has%20said%20that%20such%20apps%20violate%20its%20terms%20of%20service.%20Lyft%20has%20gone%20further%2C%20suggesting%20that%20it%20could%20deactivate%20the%20accounts%20of%20gig%20workers%20found%20to%20be%20using%20the%20apps.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20game%2C%20players%20are%20shown%20a%20series%20of%20ride-hailing%20trips%2C%20including%20total%20pay%2C%20the%20distance%20of%20the%20trip%2C%20how%20far%20they'd%20have%20to%20drive%20to%20pick%20up%20the%20passenger%2C%20and%20how%20long%20the%20gig%20would%20take%20to%20complete.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20tutorial%20at%20the%20start%20advises%20players%20that%20their%20costs%2C%20such%20as%20fuel%2C%20come%20out%20to%2075%20cents%20a%20mile%2C%20so%20any%20trips%20that%20they%20accept%20will%20need%20to%20gross%20more%20than%20that.%20Players%20also%20have%20eight%20hours%20of%20driving%20time%20in%20which%20to%20make%20their%20%24200%20profit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPlayers%20have%20five%20seconds%20to%20evaluate%20each%20trip%20and%2C%20like%20a%20dating%20app%2C%20either%20swipe%20right%20to%20take%20it%20or%20left%20to%20reject%20it.%20While%20some%20trips%20are%20clear%20winners%20%E2%80%94%20such%20as%20one%20that%20pays%20almost%20%2426%20for%2015%20minutes%20of%20work%20and%20a%20few%20miles%20of%20driving%20%E2%80%94%20others%20require%20a%20closer%20analysis.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInada%20said%20that%20he%20hopes%20players%20who%20regularly%20take%