omy%20and%20Impact%20Innovations%2C%20CEEW%2C%20is%20of%20the%20opinion%20that%20this%20plunge%20in%20prices%20is%20making%20green%20applications%20affordable.%20%E2%80%9CPeople%20have%20started%20realising%20that%20solar%20can%20be%20harnessed%20for%20so%20many%20other%20productive%20applications%20beyond%20consumptive%20use%20in%20rural%20areas.%20The%20missing%20gap%20was%20how%20to%20make%20these%20appliances%20efficient%3B%20we%E2%80%99ve%20been%20trying%20to%20solve%20for%20this%20by%20creating%20energy-efficient%20appliances.%E2%80%9D%20These%20appliances%20are%20now%20creating%20quite%20a%20stir%20in%20the%20villages%20where%20they%20are%20being%20introduced.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20plausible%20reason%20could%20be%20the%20increased%20earnings%20following%20DRE%20tech%20adoption.%20As%20pointed%20out%20by%20a%20CEEW%20report%2C%2090%20percent%20of%20those%20who%20adopted%20a%20DRE%20solution%20reported%20income%20growth%2C%20typically%20achieving%20an%20annual%20income%20of%20INR%2040%2C000%20(with%20an%20average%20usage%20of%20eight%20months)%2C%20a%2033%20percent%20increase%20compared%20to%20their%20baseline%20earnings.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20earnings%20are%20one%20side%20of%20the%20story%2C%20the%20other%20side%20is%20expenditure.%20Naveen%20admits%20he%E2%80%99d%20never%20have%20been%20able%20to%20afford%20the%20%3Cem%3Eatta%20chakki%3C%2Fem%3E%20if%20it%20weren%E2%80%99t%20for%20a%20subsidy%20scheme.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20%3Cem%3Eatta%20chakki%3C%2Fem%3E%20cost%20Rs%2010%20lakh.%20Almost%2050%20percent%20of%20this%20cost%20was%20borne%20by%20DD%20Solar%20Solutions%2C%20and%20I%20only%20had%20to%20pay%20Rs%205%2C20%2C000%20%E2%80%94%20which%20I%20am%20paying%20back%20through%20an%20EMI%20option%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20economics%20of%20going%20solar%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEconomic%20relief%20is%20key%2C%20Naveen%20explains.%20In%20fact%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20also%20what%20g