the%20country%20would%20be%20familiar%20with%20a%20solar%20panel%20for%20mobile%20charging%2C%20or%20a%20solar%20lantern%2C%20they%20might%20not%20imagine%20that%20solar%20could%20be%20used%20to%20grow%20fodder%20or%20as%20a%20cold%20storage%20solution.%20So%20the%20awareness%20gap%20is%20pretty%20big.%20Until%20they%20actually%20see%20it%20in%20action%2C%20it%20might%20prove%20difficult%20for%20them%20to%20decide%20to%20buy%20it.%20That%E2%80%99s%20where%20the%20Powering%20Livelihoods%20programme%20comes%20in%3B%20we%20invite%20them%20to%20witness%20successful%20models.%20These%20demo%20champions%20%E2%80%94%20early%20adopters%20of%20the%20solution%20%E2%80%94%20then%20demonstrate%20the%20technology%20to%20others%20in%20their%20area.%20Speaking%20to%20existing%20users%20gives%20them%20perspective%20and%20builds%20their%20confidence.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENaveen%20is%20a%20case%20in%20point.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrior%20to%20seeking%20out%20a%20solar-powered%20%3Cem%3Eatta%20chakki%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20he%20gauged%20the%20pulse%20of%20the%20market%20by%20speaking%20to%20other%20micro-preneurs%20who%E2%80%99d%20taken%20the%20leap%20from%20diesel%20to%20solar.%20He%20judges%20success%20by%20certain%20fundamental%20yardsticks%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDoes%20it%20work%20well%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20is%20the%20efficiency%20like%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAre%20you%20happy%20with%20your%20decision%3F%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20his%20confidence%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F282854%2Fmaharashtra-family-solar-drying-machine-food-processing-chikoo-increases-sales%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esolar-powered%20device%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20reflected%20in%20the%20steady%20whirr%20of%20the%20machine%20that%20earns%20him%20Rs%2060%2C000%2Fmonth.%20After%20accounting%20for%20the%20maintenance%20costs%2C%20which%20go%20up%20to%20Rs%2010%2C000%20a%20month%2C%20Naveen%20says%20his%20net%20profit%20is%20around%20Rs%2050%2C000%20a%20month.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20adapting%20technologies%20for%20a%20semi-urban%20or%20rural%20market%20is%20crucial%2C%20Tushar%20reasons.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20an%20urban%20setting%2C%20solar%20is%20more%20for%20cost%20savings.%20Battery%20storage%20isn%E2%80%99t%20as%20crucial.%20But%20this%20changes%20when%20you%20talk%20about%20a%20rural%20audience.%20They%20need%20battery%20storage.%20Then%20there%E2%80%99s%20also%20the%20part%20about%20ensuring%20that%20the%20EMIs%20are%20paid%20on%20time%20so%20that%20their%20credit%20score%20isn%E2%80%99t%20affected.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20where%20he%20says%20financial%20literacy%20is%20key.%20DD%20Solar%20Solutions%20has%20a%20network%20of%20business%20associates%20%E2%80%94%20people%20trusted%20in%20the%20community%20%E2%80%94%20who%20see%20to%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20technology%20on%20the%20ground.%20Their%20impact%20has%20fanned%20out%20across%20the%20country%20with%20over%201%2C800%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fgoogle.com%2Fsearch%3Fq%3Dsolar%2Brefrigerator%2Bthe%2Bbetter%2Bindia%26rlz%3D1C1YTUH_enIN1048IN1048%26oq%3Dsolar%2Brefrigerator%2Bthe%2Bbetter%2Bindia%26gs_lcrp%3DEgZjaHJvbWUyBggAEEUYOTIGCAEQRRg80gEINjI0MGowajSoAgCwAgA%26sourceid%3Dchrome%26ie%3DUTF-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einstallations%20of%20the%20solar%20refrigerator%3C%2Fa%3E%20pan%20India%2C%20and%20over%2040%20solar%20%3Cem%3Eatta%20chakkis%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Through%20its%20clean%20tech%20solutions%20and%20a%20robust%20mechanism%20of%20encouraging%20adoptions%2C%20DD%20Solar%20is%20scripting%20a%20new%20age%20India%20where%20possibility%20and%20sustainability%20live%20side%20by%20side.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAll%20pictures%20courtesy%20DD%20Solar%20Solutions%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESourc