nclude%20setting%20up%20a%20seven-ton%20biogas%20plant%20to%20convert%20wet%20waste%20to%20CNG%20and%20enable%20all%20civic%2F%20police%20vehicles%20in%20our%20ward%20to%20run%20on%20CNG%2C%20free%20of%20cost.%20Our%20work%20will%20never%20stop.%20There%20will%20always%20be%20something%20to%20do%2C%E2%80%9D%20avers%20Madhu.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EWritten%20by%20Janaki%20Krishnamoorthi%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1756376823000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fpali-hill-1690870702.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D492950%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Pali%20Hill%20Residents%E2%80%99s%20Association%20began%20with%20eight%20women%20in%20the%2090s%20who%20dreamt%20of%20transforming%20their%20neighbourhood%20into%20a%20cleaner%2C%20greener%2C%20and%20safer%20home.%20The%20members%20recall%20how%20they%20achieved%20this%20award-winning%20transformation%20over%20two%20decades.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Guest%20Contributor%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F492950%2Fmumbai-pali-hill-women-sustainable-green-neighbourhood%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Sisters%20in%20Dehradun%20Pursue%20Farming%20in%2040s%2C%20Earn%20Rs%2011%20Lakh%20by%20Growing%20Gooseberry%2C%20Mangoes%20%26amp%3B%20More%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ESisters%20in%20Dehradun%20Pursue%20Farming%20in%2040s%2C%20Earn%20Rs%2011%20Lakh%20by%20Growing%20Gooseberry%2C%20Mangoes%20%26amp%3B%20More%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20interviews%20and%20reporting%20for%20this%20story%20were%20conducted%20in%20May%202024.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20when%20Namita%20Rawat%20Negi%20and%20Manisha%20Gosain%2C%20two%20sisters%20from%20Dehradun%2C%20Uttarakhand%2C%20decided%20to%20pursue%20farming%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F351525%2Ffarming-profitable-how-to-make-natural-pesticides-himachal-couple-zero-budget-natural-earns-double%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etheir%20decision%20raised%20more%20eyebrows%20than%20smiles%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ca%20data-tracker%3D%5C%22%7B%26quot%3Barticle_name%26quot%3B%3A%26quot%3BArticle%20Page%20Ad%20Banner%26quot%3B%2C%26quot%3Bposition%26quot%3B%3A1%2C%26quot%3Barticle_id%26quot%3B%3A492928%7D%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcampaign.thebetterindia.com%2Ftbi-showcase%2F%5C%22%20data-carousel%3D%5C%22adbanner%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Article%20Ad%20Banner%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Fad-banner-1756106894.jpg%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fa%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20driven%20by%20their%20strong%20self-belief%20and%20a%20desire%20to%20protect%20agricultural%20land%2C%20they%20ventured%20into%20what%20is%20widely%20regarded%20as%20one%20of%20the%20toughest%20occupations%20%E2%80%94%20farming.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20journey%20demands%20immense%20perseverance%20and%20patience%2C%20but%20their%20determination%20has%20remained%20unwavering.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20their%2040s%2C%20many%20believed%20that%20Namita%20and%20Manisha%20would%20only%20dabble%20in%20farming%20for%20a%20few%20months%20before%20returning%20to%20their%20previous%20lives%20and%20jobs%3B%20possibly%20selling%20the%20land.%20However%2C%20they%20defied%20expectations%20and%20persisted%20in%20building%20their%20agricultural%20venture.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20they%20proudly%20operate%20Doon%20Gooseberry%20Farm%2C%20a%20cozy%20setup%20born%20from%20their%20dedication%20and%20passion%2C%20supported%20steadfastly%20by%20their%20husbands.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDuring%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%2C%20we%20first%20visited%20my%20sister%E2%80%99s%20land%2