have%20been%20exceptional%2C%20particularly%20in%20paddy%20fields%2C%20where%20tests%20showed%20that%20rice%20plots%20treated%20with%20our%20product%20thrived%20with%20more%20kernels%20per%20stalk.%20We%20are%20also%20experimenting%20in%20vegetable%20fields%20now%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20process%20of%20turning%20industrial%20waste%20into%20something%20that%20enriches%20the%20earth.%20It%20has%20been%20nothing%20short%20of%20a%20miracle%20for%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dr%20Sahu%20smiles%20proudly.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20products%20have%20not%20only%20regenerated%20crowded%20slums%20of%20steel%20waste%20but%20also%20brought%20livelihoods%20back%20from%20the%20brink%2C%20and%20filled%20farmers%20with%20optimism%20about%20sustainable%20agri-practices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFarmer%20Sunil%20Singh%2C%20who%20cultivates%20paddy%20on%20two%20acres%20of%20land%20in%20Odisha%E2%80%99s%20Sundargarh%20district%2C%20received%20two%20truckloads%20of%20LD-slag-based%20fertiliser%20from%20Dr%20Sahu%20during%20the%20last%20Kharif%20season.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharing%20with%20%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20grow%20paddy%20on%20about%20two%20acres%20of%20land.%20The%20paddy%20we%20planted%20matured%20in%20120%20to%20130%20days%20and%20showed%20some%20improvement%20after%20using%20the%20fertiliser.%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Fsteel-slag-fertiliser-1-1755836394.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dr%20Sahu%20was%20selected%20for%20RKVY%20(Rashtriya%20Krishi%20Vikas%20Yojana)-RAFTAAR%20that%20aims%20to%20strengthen%20the%20agriculture%20and%20allied%20sectors.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Fsteel-slag-fertiliser-1-1755836394.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Fsteel-slag-fertiliser-1-1755836394-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Fsteel-slag-fertiliser-1-1755836394-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Fsteel-slag-fertiliser-1-1755836394-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Fsteel-slag-fertiliser-1-1755836394-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-490454%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EDr%20Sahu%20was%20selected%20for%20RKVY%20(Rashtriya%20Krishi%20Vikas%20Yojana)-RAFTAAR%2C%20which%20aims%20to%20strengthen%20the%20agriculture%20and%20allied%20sectors.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20the%20economic%20benefits%20weren%E2%80%99t%20immediately%20apparent%2C%20we%20observed%20an%20increase%20in%20growth%20and%20grain%20kernel%20formation.%20We%20managed%20to%20harvest%20two%20to%20three%20quintals%20more%20paddy%20compared%20to%20the%20previous%20year%20efforts.%20Currently%2C%20we%20haven%E2%80%99t%20started%20this%20season%E2%80%99s%20paddy%20sowing%2C%20but%20we%20are%20planning%20to%20procure%20more%20fertiliser%20from%20Dr%20Sahu%20for%20the%20upcoming%20crop%20cycle%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20farmer%20Laxman%20Lakra%20from%20Birkera%20village%20of%20Sundargarh%20district%2C%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20began%20using%20this%20new%20fertiliser%20in%20my%20mango%20orchard%20this%20January.%20Earlier%2C%20I%20relied%20on%20chemical%20fertilisers%20along%20with%20cow%20dung%2C%20but%20now%20I%20use%20only%20this%20fertiliser%20and%20cow%20dung.%20The%20results%20have%20been%20remarkable.%20The%20mangoes%20are%20bigger%2C%20tastier%2C%20and%20completely%20organic.%20Because%20of%20this%2C%20I%E2%80%99m%20able%20to%20sell%20them%2